Retro Hangman Pseudo code
Generate a guess word at random
Show the user word length in " _ "
Set lives to 10
Provide alphabet for user to chose letters from
Each letter can only be guessed once per turn
If guess is correct, display letter(s) according to letter index
If user guesses entire word, display " You Won! "
If guess is wrong, -1 life each time until 0
If user lives reach 0, display " Game Over "
To reset game click "Play again" button at anytime
New word is generated and game starts over
